latestIgtvVideos.title: Full body stretching exercises for flexibility
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Stretching keeps the muscles flexible, strong, and healthy, and we need that flexibility to maintain a range of motion in the joints. Without it, the muscles shorten and become tight. Then, when you call on the muscles for activity, they are weak and unable to extend all the way. That puts you at risk for joint pain, strains, and muscle damage.
Try my full body stretching movements before any workout or you can do the same when you feel muscle/joint pain in any particular area of your body.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Produced for @foxy.famous
Here is a basic skincare routine to always have amazing skin :
1. Wash your face at least twice a day
2. Scrub/Exfoliate your face once or twice in a week
3. Use Good moisturizer after cleansing
4. Use a good sunscreen cream before stepping out of your home.
5. Keep yourself hydrated, at least 3-4 liters of water on a daily basis and have a well-balanced diet and take care of multivitamins sply Vit. C and Vit. E for skin.
